{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"57750-the-lost-ball","title":"Ang Nawawalang Bola","description":"Gusto makipaglaro ni Jomar sa kaniyang mga kaibigan. Pero hindi niya makita ang kaniyang bola sa makalat niyang kuwarto! Gaano katagal kayang makapaghihintay ang kaniyang mga kaibigan?","language":"Filipino","langCode":"fil","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kaye Sucgang"],"illustrators":["ASM Tanvir Hassan Raju"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/57750-the-lost-ball"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93521/size3/495d9fd5d7c96ad806177b340988f891.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93521/size6/495d9fd5d7c96ad806177b340988f891.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73003/size6/6c9c1cf9da843d1d663207aab1b2c7be.jpg","text":"Handa nang maglaro sina Sammy, Marcus, Errol at Jomar. \nSabi ni Jomar, \"Teka lang! Kukunin ko ang bola ko.\"","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73004/size6/f78ca44e75feb8211c758e7569aba3af.jpg","text":"Tumakbo si Jomar \nsa kaniyang kuwarto.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73005/size6/768c47159d6ae997cfb36f4021111750.jpg","text":"Uh-oh!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/79590/size6/f551152f6b211f110928703b2ccdf792.jpg","text":"Saan kaya dapat unang hanapin ni Jomar ang kaniyang bola?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73007/size6/b3a607b0ffe750df6f9543cb0933c1f7.jpg","text":"Nasa ibabaw kaya ng kama ang bola?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73008/size6/5e4ef7d052e76ae8f1b423336ea6c166.jpg","text":"Hindi, \nwala sa ibabaw ng kama!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73009/size6/f28481727e676807ad470a044542558b.jpg","text":"Nasa ibabaw kaya ng mesa ang bola?","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73010/size6/9a8639e08a941fd27e8fa345f749ed72.jpg","text":"Hindi,\nwala sa ibabaw \nng mesa!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73013/size6/865b1d28afb29d10107477f792e98e17.jpg","text":"\"Jomar, bilisan mo na!\" tawag ni Sammy.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73014/size6/5aa87ed4bc479ecae152c28810c3e754.jpg","text":"Sumigaw mula sa kuwarto si Jomar,\n\"Antay lang!\nHindi ko mahanap ang bola ko!\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73016/size6/c7550a51789870e3cfe3df080753a2f1.jpg","text":"Malapit kaya ang bola \nsa sabitan\nng mga damit?\nNasa ilalim kaya ito \nng mga damit?","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73018/size6/5562ce69cabeff2ab72efb9496b9c252.jpg","text":"Hindi!\nWala rin dito ang bola!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73019/size6/b56fa097dc04bdc331e3494b4c7cac26.jpg","text":"Sumigaw sina Sammy, Marcus at Errol.\n\"Nababagot na kami. Ayaw na naming maghintay! Aalis na kami, Jomar!\"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73021/size6/6d2c04782c7521d5f9e2942b0c492cb3.jpg","text":"15/19","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73022/size6/4ab08d8fe5c5cf59ab6040ef29481fce.jpg","text":"Naiinis na sarili niya si Jomar. Hindi kasi niya mahanap ang bola kahit saan!\nPero nagmumukhang mas malinis naman ang kuwarto niya...","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73023/size6/3852423e82f4b373258d1e37495f7577.jpg","text":"...maliban sa isang kahon,\nna nakalagay sa itaas ng aparador...","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73024/size6/c803cdce5350d45f9dbc7d8353d40a3a.jpg","text":"Tingnan mo!\nNarito pala ang bola!","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73025/size6/942f9216bf13d89e76dc8239f9a33609.jpg","text":"Kinabukasan, hinanap ni Jomar ang kaniyang mga kaibigan. Ngayon, handa na ang bola niya sa paglalaro!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":177}}